These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, december, march
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, begonia, marigold
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
2. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
3. the person who growszinnia is the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Birthday   | march | june | december |
| Flower    | begonia    | marigold | zinnia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: zucchini, raspberry, cabbage
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, aristoff, siglo
1. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food       | raspberry | cabbage | zucchini |
| Cigar   | siglo    | aristoff     | bluemaster        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different pets are kept: turtle, lizard, hamster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, handball
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Pet         | hamster     | lizard | turtle |
| Sport   | snowboarding | cycling     | handball  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, 7up
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose, orchid
1. the person drinking tea is the person who growsrose##1
2. the person drinking fanta is the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Beverage   | 7up | tea  | fanta  |
| Flower         | zinnia  | rose | orchid |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, white, orange
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, cricket, biathlon
1. the person who likes orange is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who's sport is parkour##2
2. the person who likes white is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Color         | blood-red   | orange | white    |
| Sport   | cricket | biathlon     | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, milk
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, french, spanish
1. the person drinking sprite is the french##1
2. the spanish is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | milk | sprite   |
| Nationality   | spanish     | dutch    | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, coral, pink
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, february, september
1. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the person who likes white is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who likes pink##2
3. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Color   | pink | white | coral |
| Birthday           | february         | march         | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, firefighter, freelancer
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, cooking, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the videographer##2
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Job   | firefighter | freelancer | videographer |
| Hobby    | cooking    | puzzles | drawing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, go, poker
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, lettuce, grapes
1. the person eating grapes is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Game   | poker   | go  | scrabble  |
| Food         | grapes | lettuce | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, dahlia, aconite
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, montecristo, fonseca
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Flower   | daisy    | aconite      | dahlia |
| Cigar       | montecristo | fonseca | tiparillo   |

