.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
3 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, whist
3 different pets are kept: mouse, hamster, goldfish
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the owner of the mouse is the person playing canasta##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing whist is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Game         | backgammon | whist | canasta |
| Pet   | hamster | goldfish   | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, skateboarding, golf
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, water
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
4. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Sport   | golf | skateboarding | soccer |
| Beverage     | 7up     | iced-tea   | water        |

