.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, rock-climbing
There 3 different types of food: peach, cauliflower, avocado
1. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person eating peach is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing  | board-games | card-games   |
| Food         | cauliflower | avocado   | peach |

