.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, dunhill, oliveros
City: paris, san-francisco, edinburgh
1. the oliveros-smoker is between the dunhill-smoker and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
2. the dunhill-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Cigar   | dunhill | oliveros | prince |
| City     | paris    | edinburgh  | san-francisco   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, helicopter, scooter
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, aquamarine, ivory
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
4. the person driving the scooter is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Transport   | trike  | scooter     | helicopter |
| Color   | aquamarine | purple | ivory    |

