.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, fishing, video-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, bartender, designer
1. the designer is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the designer is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the bartender is in an odd position##4
4. the analyst is on the left or right of the bartender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Hobby          | video-games | woodworking | fishing  |
| Job   | designer      | analyst  | bartender |

