.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-17::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, jet-ski
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, country, blues
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Transport   | bus | jet-ski | motorbike    |
| Music-Genre           | country     | blues  | classical |

