.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, teacher, firefighter
House: cottage, modern, palace
1. the palace house is on the right of the chef##1
2. the chef is in the middle##1
3. the firefighter is the modern house##1
4. the cottage house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job         | firefighter | chef   | teacher |
| House   | modern   | cottage | palace      |

