.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, alhambra, aristoff
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, march, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
2. the davidoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Cigar      | davidoff | alhambra | aristoff |
| Birthday   | march   | february          | october |

