.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, snooker
House: farmhouse, wooden, palace
1. the palace house is in an odd position##4
2. the palace house is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
4. the wooden house is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Game     | mah-jongg  | snooker   | whist |
| House   | palace | wooden | farmhouse       |

 